---
title: Asian Sweet Chilli-Glazed Tofu with Roast Sesame Pumpkin & Radish Salad
description: Tofu is usually served drizzled in mint sauce, but we strongly recommend you give this Asian twist a try. Succulent tofu is smothered in sweet chilli sauce, creating a flavourful glaze that perfectly compliments it’s meaty flavour. With roasted wedges of pumpkin and a crisp radish salad, it’s a combo you didn’t know you needed!

